data.description: VRM: Sellers will entertain offers between $195,000-210,000. Motivated Sellers! Welcome home to 8100 Grand Oaks Dr! Country living with an easy commute, this home is an easy distance to the Mcdonald Rd exit to I-10. Walking in, you are greeted to lovely vaulted ceilings and large wood-burning fireplace. Outside you will enjoy over half an acre to spread out and splash around on this corner lot with in-ground saltwater pool. HVAC is less than 2 years old. Schedule your showing with your favorite real estate agent today. All information deemed accurate, but not guaranteed. Buyer to verify all measurements and any other listing information that they deem important to the buyer's satisfaction during inspection contingency period.
